MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2003-0038. Goodlett v. Ohio Cas. Group.

Butler App. No. CA2002-04^090. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Butler County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
